    <item>
      <title>塞尔维亚通胀放缓或将降息：决策指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/serbia-seen-cutting-rates-as-inflation-eases-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[塞尔维亚决策者上个月维持基准利率不变，但该国可能利用整体通胀放缓的迹象，将利率降至近两年来的最低水平。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/serbia-seen-cutting-rates-as-inflation-eases-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>捷克央行降息，因风险笼罩未来道路：决策指南</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/czechs-to-cut-rates-as-risks-cloud-path-ahead-decision-guide</link>
      <description><![CDATA[由于目前疲软的经济增长压倒了通胀风险的担忧，捷克决策者可能会继续连续第八次降息。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/czechs-to-cut-rates-as-risks-cloud-path-ahead-decision-guide</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 05:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>市场关注刺激措施 中国大宗商品进口表现坚挺</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/china-s-commodities-imports-resilient-as-markets-eye-stimulus</link>
      <description><![CDATA[周四发布的海关数据显示，10月份中国原材料进口大多同比增长，尽管经济放缓，但需求依然保持强劲。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/china-s-commodities-imports-resilient-as-markets-eye-stimulus</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 04:52:05 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>中国要求银行降低银行间存款利率以促进增长</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/china-tells-banks-to-cut-interbank-deposit-rates-to-boost-growth</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据知情人士透露，中国监管机构要求国内银行降低对其他金融机构存款的利率，以释放资金来提振经济。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-11-07/china-tells-banks-to-cut-interbank-deposit-rates-to-boost-growth</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 07 Nov 2024 04:50:38 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
